title: Pyramid Solitaire Egypt v1.0.14
description:
Help the Pharaoh and his queen build the ancient and glorious pyramids in this solitaire game.

Set in the glory days of Egypt, you must remove all the cards from the layout to construct these ancient wonders of the world.

FEATURES
- addictive gameplay
- enchanting graphics set in ancient Egypt
- simple controls, easy to learn
- atmospheric sound effects

If you like to relax with a card game or puzzle game then we think you'll love Pyramid Solitaire Ancient Egypt.
